title: Bobby’s Dog Experiences First Big Thunderstorm + Favorite 90’s Song Draft + Eddie’s Son Calls Him a Liar
itunes:title: Bobby’s Dog Experiences First Big Thunderstorm + Favorite 90’s Song Draft + Eddie’s Son Calls Him a Liar
description:
Bobby’s dog had to hop in the bed with him last night during a thunderstorm. We do our fantasy draft of our favorite songs from the 90's. Eddie’s son says he was spreading fake news about him on the show.
